	<section id="recipe">
		<p>
			Children love nutella. Adults love nutella. The French
			eat it with their crÃªpes; the kids with everything. So
			why not you?  
			Oh right, because it's unhealthy, and since you've come
			to <span class="nm">Lila, Chop!</span> for recipes, then you certainly care
			about that!  
			Well, how about protein-nutella
			served clean, healthy, and deliciously nutritious?
		</p>
		<table class="ingredients">
			<caption>Ingredients</caption>
			<thead>
				<tr>
					<th class="amount" colspan="2">amount</th>
					<th class="name">name</th>
				</tr>
			</thead>
			<tr>
				<td class="amount" data-lilachop-amount="1"></td>
				<td class="unit">scoop</td>
